metadata.description: With sports as his primary outlet throughout his upbringing, professional athlete Ricardo Louis was searching for another means of improving his daily life and mental health. Using the artistic pseudonym PAPO, he began focusing on his artwork as his preferred mode of expression. In “No Service,” PAPO creates his first-ever fully hybrid piece for NFT.NYC 2022 as part of One of None’s Hybrid Gallery.
metadata.name: No Service
